(Attach a screenshot or GIF of your project here if possible)

## 🏗 How to Run
1. Clone the repository:
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/shrutideshmukh788/live-cohert-JS-DOM-.git
   ```
2. Open the **index.html** file in a browser.
3. Click the button to generate random colors!

## 🌟 Learning Outcomes
- Improved JavaScript skills in **DOM Manipulation & Event Listeners**.
- Gained hands-on experience with **randomization** in web applications.
- Applied **Template Literals** for better code readability.

